name: help
description: Displays a message with the currently available commands.

name: ping
description: Displays the discord API's current latency.

name: ping-db
description: Displays the current latency between the bot and it's database.

name: server
description: Provides information about the current server.

name: user
description: Provides information about a specified user.

name: translate
description: Translates a message from any language to any language.

name: say
description: Makes the bot say a specified message.

name: coinflip
description: Let's you bet a specified amout of money on heads or tais. You have a 50/50 percent chance of doubling or losing your bet

name: randompic
description: Send a random picture using the [picsum.photos](https://picsum.photos/) API.

name: randomfeet
description: I have nothing to say about my greatest shame...

name: 911-countdown
description: Displays huw much time is left until Spetember 11th.

name: work
description: Lets you work for a random amount of money.

name: beg
description: Lets you beg for a random (or no) amount of money.

name: rob
description: Steals a random amount of money from the target user, and adds it to your balance.

name: balance
description: Displays the user's current bank and handheld balance.

name: deposit
description: Deposits money into the user's bank account. It has a daily limit for free deposits, but the users can choose to pay a small deposit fee if they exceed the limit.

name: withdraw
description: Withdraws money from the user's bank account.

name: pay
description: Transfers money from one user to another.

name: roulette
description: Lets you pick a color, then gives you a great price if you guess the color right.

name: leaderboard
description: Displays users with the most money on the server.

name: warn
description: Warns a specified member on the server.

name: timeout
description: Times out a specified member for a specified time.

name: kick
description: Kicks a specified member from the server.

name: ban
description: Bans a specified member from the server.

name: purge
description: Purges (mass deletes) a specified amount of messages from the current channel.

name: config-autorole
description: Sets / modifies / disables the autorole feature. When a new member joins the server, a specified role will get assigned to them automatically.

name: config-welcome
description: Sets / modifies / disables the welcome messages feature. When a new member joins the server, the bot send a specified welcome message.

name: config-logging
description: Sets / modifies / disables the channel where event on the server will get logged

name: config-bridge
description: Sets / modifies / disables bridging all messages from one channel to another.

name: rename
description: Renames a specified user to a specified nickname in the current server.

name: slowmode
description: Sets / disables the slowmode for a specified channel.

name: config-goodbye
description: Sets / modifies / disables the goodbye messages feature. When a member leaves the server, the bot send a specified goodbye message.

name: coinflip-fun
description: Flips a coin that has a 50/50 chance landing on heads or tails. Has an economy (*/coinflip*) version with gambling.

name: blackjack
description: Lets you play a game of blackjack with a specified amount. You can pick **Hit** or **Stand** until the player or the house wins

name: config-darwin
description: Sets / modifies / disables Darwin's occasional video scraping & posting feature.

name: cigany
description: Says "fuj" and sends a random pic of a "person" from a specific race.

name: cooldown
description: Lets you check your or other users economy cooldowns for all or a specified economy command.
